com.amplifyframework.datastore.syncengine

Class MutationQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.datastore.syncengine.MutationQueue

  • public final class MutationQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    The MutationQueue is a LinkedHashMap like container , the goal of using this container is to achieve O(1) time complexity for both getting a PendingMutation and update an existing mutation with valid id. MutationQueue is implementing the Queue interface and provide most of the queue operations,
